          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In the present study the experimental statistics",
                " for the reaction d(g,PI0pn) accumulated at VEPP-3",
                " in 2013 was used. Unlike the previous measurements,",
                " the main goal of the last experiment was to study",
                " the coherent PI0 photoproduction on a",
                " tenzor-polarized deuterium target using an",
                " unpolarized photon beam. In contrast to the",
                " experiment of 2003, in which only two final nucleons",
                " were detected, in the present case the proton and two",
                " g-quanta from the PI0 decay were detected in",
                " coincidence."
              ]
            }
          ],
